iMsM__DhuDg.title: 112년 동안 진짜 처음. 너무 궁금해서 항구 바닥에 집게 넣어봤더니┃충격적인 해양쓰레기 실태┃목포항 악취┃극한직업┃#골라듄다큐
iMsM__DhuDg.description:
※ 이 영상은 2009년 7월 29일에 방송된 ＜극한직업 - 해양 폐기물 수거반 1부＞의 일부입니다.

항구에 드나드는 선박들의 안전을 지키는 숨은 파수꾼.
바다의 오염을 막는 바다 청소부.
쓰레기를 찾아 비가 오나, 눈이 오나 바다로 나가는 사람들, 그들의 직업은 해양 폐기물 수거원이다.
바다 위를 떠다니는 작은 부표, 소량의 폐그물도 배의 프로펠러에 들어가면 대형 사고를 일으킬 수 있는 위험 요소가 된다. 
그 때문에 이른 아침부터 야간까지 항구와 먼바다를 순찰하며, 쓰레기를 수거한다.
그런가 하면 수면 아래, 오랫동안 침적된 수천 톤의 쓰레기를 끊임없이 물 위로 끌어올려야 하는 작업도 있는데, 석탄처럼 검은 개펄에 뒤덮인 오물과 고철, 낡은 어구들이 내뿜는 지독한 악취와 악천후를 견뎌야 하는 극한의 작업이 반복된다.
끝이 보이지 않는 쓰레기와의 전쟁. 해양 폐기물 수거 현장으로 찾아가 본다.

바다 밑에 쓰레기 장이 있다. 수중 침적 폐기물 수거
우리나라의 수중 침적 폐기물은 약 40만 톤 이상으로 추정된다.
하지만, 여기에 매년 16만 톤 이상이 더해지고 있는 실정이다. 이런 해양 폐기물은 어업 생산성을 떨어뜨리고, 해양 오염의 주범이 된다.
그리하여 지난 6월부터, 목포항이 112년 만에 수중 침적 폐기물 수거에 들어갔다.
바다 밑에 오랫동안 버려져 있던 폐타이어와 어망, 통발 그리고 생활쓰레기가 끊임없이 올라와, 작업 40일 만에 1천7백 톤이라는 엄청난 양의 쓰레기가 수거됐다.
90톤급 대형 크레인과 수백 킬로그램이 넘는 쓰레기가 머리 위로 넘나드는 위험천만한 작업 환경에서, 악취와 악천후를 견디는 바다 청소부들을 만나본다.

일촉즉발, 극한의 작업 현장
한순간의 실수가 대형 사고로 이어질 수 있는 위험천만한 작업 현장.
부선 위에서 대형 크레인과 포크레인, 그리고 사람이 함께 작업을 하는데 수거 원들의 안전을 위해 꼭 필요한 것이 바로 수신호다. 
크레인에 달린 집게가 부선 위를 가로지를 때, 수신호가 안 맞아 사람을 치거나, 집게에서 떨어지는 쓰레기에게 맞으면 그들은 '즉사'한다고 이야기한다.
그래서 작업장은 항상 긴장감이 맴돈다.
석탄처럼 검은 개펄에 뒤덮여 형체를 알 수 없는 쓰레기들이 부선 위로 올라오면, 고철은 따로 분류하고 개펄도 큰 포대에 담아 따로 인양한다. 나머지 폐기물은 육지로 이송되는데.
육지로 쓰레기를 옮기던 크레인이 갑자기 멈췄다. 크레인의 와이어가 뚝 끊어져 버리는 사고가 일어났는데... 설상가상 폭우가 밀려오고, 빗속에서 그들은 안전하게 작업을 마칠 수 있을까?

가족, 그 뜨거운 이름
목포 폐기물 수거 반 직원들은 작업하는 기간은 부선 안에서 먹고, 자고 모든 생활을 함께한다.
가족들과 함께 지내는 시간보다 직원들과 지내는 시간이 더 많기에 언제부턴가 서로에게 또 다른 가족이 되었다.
하지만, 마음 한켠에는 떨어져 있는 가족들에 대한 미안함과 그리움이 자리 잡고 있는데.
가족을 위해 땀 흘려 일하는 자랑스러운 '가장'들을 만나본다.

lXv8C0m_9gA.description:
Merci à Yfood de soutenir la chaîne. Allez voir leurs produits en cliquant sur mon lien : https://bit.ly/yfood_Mathador_Tasterpacks

Allez voir la première partie de cette vidéo chez l'ami Astronogeek : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rUUqyxMcyOA

L'histoire de la plongée sous-marine, c'est l'histoire de l'Humain. Aller découvrir de nouveaux territoires. Toujours plus haut, toujours plus loin. et pour ce qui nous interesse aujourd'hui : Toujours plus profond. Quitte à devoir défier les lois physiques étranges qui régissent les profondeurs. Découvrez comment au fil des siècles l'être humain a peu à peu atteint son objectif un peu fou : respirer sous l'eau.

► POUR SOUTENIR LA CHAÎNE :

https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Cdx0C1Mrbe55dATnJv9lnOw_m4oGq-0BeLbEv-fGBMI/edit?usp=sharing

► ERRATUM
• 15:53 Lavoisier est né en 1743, pas 1643 !
• une précision, l'azote de l'air c'est N2 , et non "N" comme indiqué dans le montage.
• L'idiot que je suis a fait une erreur de conversion à la fin : 332m est égal à 0.33 km, pas 0.033 km
• A 15:58 il y a une illustration qui peut être confusante : J'illustre le CO2 avec un atome de carbone en rouge et deux atomes d'oxygène en noir (c'est plutôt l'inverse qui est fait d'habitude), ce qui pourrait etre pris comme une molécule de C2O au lieu de CO2
• Décidemment c'est le festival des erreurs, cette vidéo : Jules Verne. Sans le "S" à Verne ! Désolé Jules!

E69QpAsqOVs.title: Un historien de la Seconde Guerre mondiale analyse des films | Science vs Fiction
E69QpAsqOVs.description:
Profitez de l’offre exclusive de Green-Got avec 3 mois offerts en utilisant le code EXPLOREMEDIA : https://bit.ly/4hVHrbx

Dans ce nouvel épisode de Science vs Fiction, Guillaume Pollack, docteur en Histoire contemporaine et Arlette Testyler, rescapée de la Rafle du Vélodrome d’Hiver et du camp de Beaune-la-Rolande, analysent des films et séries sur la Seconde Guerre mondiale.

De "La Rafle" à "La Chute" en passant par "Jojo Rabbit" et "Il faut sauver le soldat Ryan" ... à quel point ces films sont-ils réalistes ?
Comment la guerre a débuté ? Les Allemands étaient-ils tous nazis ? Comment le régime de Vichy a collaboré ? Comment s'est passé réellement le Débarquement de Normandie ? Comment a-t-on découvert les camps de concentration ?

Exceptionnellement dans cet épisode, Arlette Testyler, présidente de l’Union des déportés d’Auschwitz, a accepté de témoigner de son expérience. Un immense merci à elle pour son témoignage.

Arlette Testyler est auteure des livres : “J'avais 9 ans quand ils nous ont raflés” (2024) et “Les enfants aussi” (2010). 
Guillaume Pollack est auteur du livre “L'armée du silence. Histoire des réseaux de résistance en France (1940-1945)". 

Un grand merci à eux pour leur participation.

hbz_cartN-c.title: 2 journalistes qui ont mené l'enquête sur Betharram racontent - C Ce Soir du 19 février 2025
hbz_cartN-c.description:
Pour voir la suite du débat 👉 https://bit.ly/BetharramScandaledEtat

Pour voir d'autres émissions 👉 https://bit.ly/CCeSoir
_________________________________________________________________
Retour sur le scandale Notre-Dame-de-Bétharram. Après plus d’un demi-siècle de silence, la France sort enfin du déni face aux nombreuses violences pratiquées au sein de l’établissement surnommé le “goulag des Pyrénées”

Nous allons essayer de comprendre ce soir, au-delà des polémiques partisanes, ce que Bétharram raconte de nous. Une faillite politique, judiciaire ? Un nouvel exemple de l’omerta qui règne dans l’Église ? Ou plus largement : une affaire qui dévoile la banalité des violences faites aux enfants dans notre société ? Nous allons en débattre ce mercredi 19 février 2025 avec : 

▶︎ Veronique MARGRON Présidente de la Conférence des religieux et religieuses de France
▶︎ America LOPEZ Journaliste France 3 Aquitaine
▶︎ Antton ROUGET Journaliste Mediapart
▶︎ Denis SALAS Magistrat
▶︎ Pascal GELIE ancien élève du lycée Notre-Dame de Betharram, témoin et victime de violences (l’un des représentants a avoir rencontré F Bayrou samedi dernier)
▶︎ Eve SIMONET réalisatrice du documentaire “Ré-inventer l’enfance”

RQ-QBX69IZo.title: Entrevista exclusiva com a grávida de Taubaté | Domingo Legal (23/02/25)
RQ-QBX69IZo.description:
No Domingo Legal a "Grávida de Taubaté" quebra o silêncio e fala pela primeira na TV após 13 anos. Celso Portiolli encontra pessoalmente Maria Verônica para uma conversa franca a respeito do caso que chocou o Brasil em 2012, além de toda a repercussão e os impactos disso em sua vida desde então.

Portiolli pergunta de forma direta se ela acha que as pessoas irão acreditar em suas palavras. “Eu não espero que elas acreditem em mim, mas eu espero que elas ouçam aquilo que eu vim para falar. O acreditar ou não acreditar nós temos o livre arbítrio”, afirma. Sobre o fato que a tornou nacionalmente famosa, comenta: “Eu nunca disse a ninguém que eu era uma coitadinha. Perdi a vida, vamos dizer assim. Eu vivi 13 anos no meu silêncio”.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

31H5fhCwutM.title: Vinicius Jr. acaba com JEJUM DE GOLS, Modric brilha com GOLAÇO, e Real Madrid bate Girona em LALIGA
31H5fhCwutM.description:
O Real Madrid segue à caça do Barcelona na disputa pelo título de LALIGA.

Mesmo sobrando em campo e empilhando chances desperdiçadas, os merengues ficaram no 2 a 0 diante do Girona, neste domingo (23), no Santiago Bernabéu, e colaram nos catalães na liderança do Campeonato Espanhol.

Os rivais somam agora 54 pontos, mas os culés levam vantagem nos critérios de desempate.

O resultado em casa nasceu com um golaço de Luka Modric, ainda na reta final da 1ª etapa e com um chutaço na entrada da área após lance de escanteio.

Já no segundo tempo, após empilhar chances, os merengues ampliaram com Vinicius Jr., que complementou passe açucarado de Mbappé às costas da defesa.

5CVj41dtkIA.title: The Chosen: Last Supper Official Trailer (Season 5)
5CVj41dtkIA.description:
The Chosen Season 5 in theaters March 28
---
I think I'm more excited to deliver this trailer than any we've done. Which isn't a coincidence because I feel the same way about Season Five as a whole. This is our most kick-butt content yet because we cover joy, pain, loyalty, betrayal, excitement, anger, sadness, and fear, sometimes within one episode.

It’s Holy Week, the most impactful and famous week in human history. Jerusalem is a powder keg with all of Jesus’ followers, enemies, and over a million Passover pilgrims packed into one small place. He shows sides of Himself we’ve never seen till now—turning over tables, literally cracking the whip, and weeping with heartbreak but also love. He also confuses His followers at every turn...and to what end?

The takeaway for you from this season: Can you believe and follow even when you don't understand?

Yes, it’s sad and heartbreaking because we’re getting closer to the cross, but we’re also going to get to see some of the most iconic and deeply moving moments from Scripture. The triumphal entry, the turning of the tables, the betrayal by Judas, and the Last Supper...all set against the biggest backdrop and sets we've ever used with a new widescreen format that demands to be seen on the big screen. But of course, we continue our obsession to humanize and authenticate everyone involved.

The table is set. I can't wait for you to see this in theaters.

Dallas Jenkins
Creator, The Chosen

ZaSUCJM3hcg.title: We Renovated An Old Warehouse Into Our Dream Studio
ZaSUCJM3hcg.description:
Thank you to all of you subscribers out there for quite frankly, making all this possible! We can’t wait to make more content for you guys over the coming months (and years) - next up, 2 videos we filmed in Malaysia!! 

HELLO FRIENDS and welcome to another video!! This week we are going to be showing you guys the ins ands outs of our entire renovation process for our new studio/office!! We have been haphazardly running around like chickens with our heads cut off for the last (8) years - and so we finally decided it was time to attempt to make our dream studio/office. And because we are huge fans of HGTV-style renovation content, we decided to renovate an old warehouse from top to bottom and document the entire process (also top to bottom). We may have bitten off more than we could chew - but we are pretty happy with how it turned out! What do you guys think of our new studio?

5BBTghKXjDE.title: Koenigsegg Jesko v Bugatti Chiron Super Sport: DRAG RACE
5BBTghKXjDE.description:
We'd like to say a huge thank you to the Al Ain Municipality (https://www.instagram.com/alainmun) and Tilal Swaihan (https://www.instagram.com/tilalswaihan) for providing the amazing drag strip, built to the highest standards to ensure safe racing and car proving away from the public roads.

Thanks, too, goes to Super Cars Majlis (https://www.instagram.com/supercarsmajlis) for inviting its amazing members along and providing the cars you see in our videos.

Also, a massive thanks goes to Ryan Griffiths at Syvecs (https://www.instagram.com/ryansyvecs) for his help in organising these races!
………………………..………………………..………………………..

We’ve just hit 10 million subscribers on YouTube, and we’re celebrating with the one you’ve all been waiting for… Bugatti vs Koenigsegg Carwow drag race! 

Mat and the team have flown out to Dubai to get their hands on these awesome hypercars, and they’re about to go head-to-head as they race over the quarter-mile for the chequered flag. But which will come out on top? Let’s take a closer look at the stats. 

Starting with the Bugatti, it’s the Chiron Super Sport, which comes with an 8-litre quad-turbo W16 that produces 1600hp and 1600Nm of torque. This power is sent to all four wheels via a 7-speed dual-clutch automatic gearbox, and the car weighs 1,995kg. Following several interior & exterior modifications, the car we have here is valued at £5,000,000.

Alongside it, we have the Koenigsegg Jesko Attack. This is powered by a 5-litre twin-turbo V8, and this creates 1280hp and 1000Nm. This power is sent to the rear wheels only via a 9-speed multi-clutch gearbox, and it weighs a whole lot less than the Bugatti, tipping the scales at just 1,420kg! But just like the Chiron Super Sport, it has a price tag of £5,000,000. 

So the Bugatti is well up on power, but it weighs half a tonne more than the Koenigsegg! Could the weight difference prove decisive? There’s only one way to find out for sure… LET’S RACE!

jNnsTNZR2bU.title: Leon Thomas: Tiny Desk Concert
jNnsTNZR2bU.description:
Bobby Carter | February 20, 2025
On the morning of Leon Thomas' Tiny Desk concert, many NPR staffers assumed the show was postponed due to a snowstorm in the D.C. area. Not only did he proactively schedule his coast-to-coast flight but he was also 30 minutes early to the office. With his sophomore album, MUTT, Thomas has planted his flag as the most exciting artist in R&B music today. The Tiny Desk had to happen now; nothing would get in the way of divine timing.

Thomas was destined to be an entertainer — he's been doing it for most of his life. His parents were both musicians and introduced him to their world early on. As an actor, he appeared in multiple Broadway plays before becoming a staple on the Nickelodeon network. Under the tutelage of Babyface, he earned his chops as a writer and producer, eventually penning and producing big hits in R&B and hip-hop.

He opens this set with three songs from MUTT and closes with two from 2023's Electric Dusk, including "Breaking Point," which he dedicates to his recently deceased grandfather, the opera singer John Anthony: "This is one of his favorite songs."

zpieZkvFnlE.title: HIGHLIGHTS Real Madrid 3-1 Man City | Mbappe (3) & Nico Goals
zpieZkvFnlE.description:
Manchester City were knocked out this season’s UEFA Champions League after a 6-3 aggregate defeat to Real Madrid.
Pep Guardiola’s side were beaten 3-1 in the second leg at the Santiago Bernabeu with Kylian Mbappe scoring a hat-trick for the current European champions.

After a 3-2 defeat in the first leg at the Etihad, City fell further behind in the tie when the Frenchman scored the opener after just four minutes.

And we suffered a further early early setback with John Stones going off injured after just eight minutes while Erling Haaland was unable to feature in the fixture.

Mbappe scored two more either side of half-time before Nico scored his first goal for City in the dying minutes.

siDLgWjq8Gk.title: Eklat im Weißen Haus: Trump und Selenskyj brechen Treffen ab
siDLgWjq8Gk.description:
Nach einem beispiellosen Streit vor laufenden Kameras haben US-Präsident Trump und sein ukrainischer Kollege Selenskyj ihr Treffen in Washington abgebrochen. Zuvor hatte Trump Selenskyj mit Vorwürfen überzogen. Dieser riskiere einen Dritten Weltkrieg.

Erst Eklat, dann Abreise: Vor laufenden Kameras haben US-Präsident Donald Trump und sein Vize JD Vance den ukrainischen Präsidenten Wolodymyr Selenskyj zurechtgewiesen. Danach wurde das Treffen abgebrochen - eigentlich hätten Trump und Selenskyj eine Rohstoffpartnerschaft unterzeichnen sollen.

Trump griff Selenskyj in scharfer Form an: "Sie setzen das Leben von Millionen Menschen aufs Spiel. Sie riskieren einen Dritten Weltkrieg", sagte Trump. Es sei respektlos von Selenskyj, auf Sicherheitszusagen der USA zu drängen.
Während einer lautstarken Auseinandersetzung warf Trump Selenskyj vor, er sei "überhaupt nicht dankbar". "Es wird schwer sein, auf diese Weise ins Geschäft zu kommen", fügte der US-Präsident hinzu.

Trump verlangte von Selenskyj, seine Haltung zu ändern. Er unterbrach ihn immer wieder, während der ukrainische Präsident versuchte, etwas zu erwidern. Stellenweise entwickelten sich heftige Wortgefechte.

Trump drohte, die Ukraine im Kampf gegen Russland im Stich zu lassen, sollte es nicht zu einer Einigung mit Kremlchef Wladimir Putin kommen. "Sie werden entweder einen Deal machen oder wir sind raus", sagte er.

FEtqiySxSH8.title: CHAOS IN DEN USA: Ein Hammer nach dem anderen! Donald Trump mischt Amerika, EU und Nato auf!
FEtqiySxSH8.description:
CHAOS IN DEN USA: Ein Hammer nach dem anderen! Donald Trump mischt Amerika, EU und Nato auf! 

Die EU hat eine entschiedene Antwort auf die von US-Präsident Donald Trump angekündigten Sonderzölle auf die Einfuhr von Autos und anderen Güter aus Europa angekündigt. Man werde umgehend auf ungerechtfertigte Hindernisse für den freien und fairen Handel reagieren, sagte ein Sprecher der zuständigen EU-Kommission in Brüssel. Dies gelte insbesondere, wenn Zölle eingesetzt würden, um eine rechtmäßige und nicht diskriminierende Politik infrage zu stellen.

Trump hatte zuvor in Washington angekündigt, eine Entscheidung über die Einführung von neuen Importzöllen auf Güter aus der EU getroffen zu haben. Diese sollten sehr bald auch öffentlich gemacht werden. Dann schob er nach: «Es werden 25 Prozent sein, allgemein gesprochen, und zwar für Autos und alle anderen Dinge.» Trump warf den Europäern dabei erneut vor, die USA auszunutzen. Die EU sei gegründet worden, «um die USA über den Tisch zu ziehen». Dies sei «der Zweck» der EU, sagte er.

8B1EtVPBSMw.title: A Minecraft Movie | Final Trailer
8B1EtVPBSMw.description:
Get ready for the greatest adventure ever built. ⛏️ Tickets are on sale NOW for #MinecraftMovie – only in theaters April 4. https://www.fandango.com/MinecraftMovie

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, “A Minecraft Movie,” directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time. 

The film also stars Emma Myers (“Wednesday”), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (“The Color Purple”), Sebastian Hansen (“Just Mercy, “Lisey’s Story”), with Jennifer Coolidge. 

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn’t just help you craft, it’s essential to one’s survival! Four misfits—Garrett “The Garbage Man” Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)—find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they’ll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black). Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative…the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (“Ninety-Five Senses,” “Nacho Libre”) directed from a screenplay by Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer and Neil Widener & Gavin James and Chris Galletta, story by Allison Schroeder and Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer, based on the Minecraft video game. Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Ólafsson and Vu Bui produced, and Todd Hallowell, Jay Ashenfelter, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza and Jon Spaihts executive produced. 

The director’s creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (“127 Hours,” “Transformers: Rise of the Beasts”), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (“The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,” “The Meg”), editor James Thomas (“Pokémon: Detective Pikachu”, the “Borat” films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (“The Jungle Book,” “The Batman”), and costume designer Amanda Neale (“The Meg,” “What We Do in the Shadows”). Casting is by Rachel Tenner. The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (“Thor: Ragnarok,” the “LEGO®” movies). 

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/Mojang Studios Production, A Jared Hess Film, “A Minecraft Movie.” The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

Bonobos are the closest living relatives of human beings, and while attempts have been made to teach them to use human language, it is very rare for human beings to try to communicate with bonobos on their terms using bonobo vocalizations and gestures, and so when I attempted to do this as an innocent visitor to this bonobo research center, the bonobos were genuinely shocked and we bonded pretty hard.

I’m running this video as a fundraiser for Ape Initiative, a federally-recognized non-profit which is the world’s only bonobo research center. Bonobos are an endangered species and Ape Initiative works with scientists and educators to help understand bonobo behavior with an aim towards ensuring their preservation in the wild. Consider donating to the fundraiser if you can or visit their website at https://www.apeinitiative.org/

kYWUF6-7uGM.title: The new stadium anthem of FC Bayern - a present by the Südkurve München 🎶
kYWUF6-7uGM.description:
Special gift for our anniversary! To mark its 125th birthday, FC Bayern is getting a new stadium anthem. Club No. 12, the fans' association and the Südkurve groups planned and organized the entire project on their own initiative.

The new stadium anthem is based on the fan chant “Always forward FC Bayern - German champions, Munich's pride. We want to celebrate in every stadium, we the fans of FCB. As it has been for over 100 years, it will remain until death: Our club, FC Bayern, in the colors white and red”.

The new anthem, which was sung by 8,000 fans in the Südkurve of the Allianz Arena after the Bundesliga home match against Heidenheim together with star tenor Jonas Kaufmann, will in future be played as the last song before the run-in at FC Bayern home matches. This special ritual created by the fans is intended to create goosebump moments and involve and involve all fans of the record champions.

“This project shows what is possible when an idea meets passion and is backed by a community full of dedication. The anthem belongs to all of us. It is the echo of our love for FC Bayern and a sign of our connection to the club's unique 125-year history,” reads a joint statement from the FCB supporters involved in the creation of the anthem. The result will be heard for the first time at the Allianz Arena in the home match against VfL Bochum on March 8.

4QxcdVrXfyc.title: Um Filme Minecraft l Trailer Final
4QxcdVrXfyc.description:
Prepare-se para a maior aventura já construída. ⛏️ #UmFilmeMinecraft 3 de abril - somente nos cinemas. 
Pré-venda a partir de 13 de março.

Um Filme Minecraft, da Warner Bros. Pictures e Legendary Pictures, estrelado por Jason Momoa e Jack Black, com direção de Jared Hess, é a primeira adaptação live-action para a telona de Minecraft, o videogame mais vendido de todos os tempos.  
O filme também é estrelado por Emma Myers (“Wandinha”); Danielle Brooks (“A Cor Púrpura”), indicada ao Oscar; Sebastian Eugene Hansen (“Luta por Justiça”, minissérie “Lisey's Story”); e Jennifer Coolidge.

Bem-vindo ao mundo do Minecraft, onde a criatividade não apenas ajuda você em suas artes e habilidades, como também é essencial para a sobrevivência! Quatro desajustados - Garrett “The Garbage Man” Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Emma Myers) e Dawn (Danielle Brooks) – envolvidos em seus problemas do dia a dia, de repente são transportados, através de um misterioso portal, para Overworld: um bizarro e cúbico país das maravilhas onde impera a imaginação. Para voltar para casa, eles vão ter que saber tudo deste mundo (além de protegê-lo de criaturas malignas como Piglins e Zumbis) ao embarcar em uma missão mágica na companhia de um experiente construtor imprevisível, Steve (Black). Juntos nessa aventura, o quinteto será desafiado a ousar e se reconectar com as qualidades únicas que os fazem, cada um deles, extraordinariamente criativos... as mesmas habilidades das quais eles precisam para prosperar no mundo real. 

Jared Hess (“Ninety-Five Senses”, “Nacho Libre: Tudo pela Crianças”), indicado ao Oscar, dirigiu Um Filme Minecraft a partir de um roteiro de Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer, Neil Widener & Gavin James, e Chris Galletta, com argumento de Allison Schroeder, Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer, baseado no videogame Minecraft. A produção é de Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Ólafsson e Vu Bui, e Todd Hallowell, Jay Ashenfelter, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza e Jon Spaihts são os produtores executivos. 

A equipe de produção criativa do diretor Jared Ness atrás das câmeras inclui o diretor de fotografia indicado ao BAFTA, Enrique Chediak (“127 Horas”, “Transformers: O Despertar das Feras”); o designer de produção vencedor do Oscar, Grant Major (“O Senhor dos Anéis: O Retorno do Rei”, “Megatubarão”); o editor James Thomas (“Pokémon: Detetive Pikachu”, os filmes “Borat”); o supervisor de efeitos visuais vencedor do Oscar, Dan Lemmon (“Mogli: O Menino Lobo”, “Batman”); a figurinista Amanda Neale (“Megatubarão”, “O Que Fazemos nas Sombras”); e a diretora de elenco, Rachel Tenner.  Os supervisores musicais são Gabe Hilfer e Karyn Rachtman, e a trilha sonora foi composta por Mark Mothersbaugh (“Thor: Ragnarok”, os filmes “LEGO”).

A Warner Bros. Pictures e a Legendary Pictures apresentam uma produção da Vertigo Entertainment, On The Roam e Mojang Studios, dirigida por Jared Hess, Um Filme Minecraft, que será distribuído nos cinemas e nas salas Imax de todo o mundo pela Warner Bros. Pictures, e na China, pela Legendary East, com estreia no Brasil marcada para 3 de abril de 2025.

Minh’alma Engrandece ao Senhor, clássico gospel composto por @asaphrsborba em 1985, ganha uma nova interpretação nas vozes de @rachelnovaesoficial e @thamiresgarciaoficial. Esta é sexta faixa do projeto de Rachel gravado ao vivo nos Estados Unidos, que reúne sete canções, entre elas, Em Teus Braços Estou Seguro, Tudo Que Mais Quero, Mil Motivos, com @fernandinho, e os medleys Alegria / Sou Feliz e Obrigado Jesus Pelo Seu Sangue / Alvo Mais Que a Neve.

“Fico feliz de ter a oportunidade de gravar com a Thamires neste projeto tão especial e por resgatar Minha Alma Engrandece, escrito ainda na década de 80, mas que continua tocando os nossos corações até hoje”, declarou Rachel sobre a intérprete de diversos hits como “Aquieta Minh’alma” e “Até Que o Senhor Venha”, do Ministério Zoe, e “A Tua Mesa Cura”.

A canção de Asaph Borba, um dos pioneiros da música cristã contemporânea no Brasil, se uniu a uma das composições de maior sucesso de Rachel Novaes, “Adorado”, que foi lançada no início de sua trajetória. Entre seus louvores de adoração mais conhecidos estão: Tua é a Glória, O Amor de Deus (Logo Eu), com @BarukTV, Comigo Estás, Tua Graça me Basta, Jesus é o Centro, com Julia Vitoria, e Ele Vem Pra Te Salvar, que faz parte do DVD que celebrou os 30 anos de ministério de @AdhemardeCamposOFICIAL. Não deixe de conferir Minh’alma Engrandece ao Senhor.

wCNq7Tkz3NU.title: 너무 쉬워 매일 먹는 두부요리 2가지! 두부는 아침 저녁 이렇게 드세요~ 맛있는데 살은 저절로 빠져요  🥇💯두부팽이버섯요리 두부계란요리
wCNq7Tkz3NU.description:
📢묘식당 인스타그램  https://www.instagram.com/myo_sikdang/

1. 두부 팽이버섯 요리

✅ 재료
두부 1모 350g
대파 흰부분 1대
팽이버섯 1봉
청양고추 2개
소금 약간 (물기 뺄 때)
올리브유

✅ 간장양념
진간장 2스푼
물 4스푼
굴소스 0.5스푼
알룰로스 또는 올리고당 1스푼
다진마늘 1스푼
참기름, 후추, 통깨

✅ 만드는 순서
1. 두부 한모는 6등분해서 키친타올위에 올리고 소금 살짝 뿌려 물기를 뺀다.

2. 대파는 세로로 반을 자르고 손가락 길이로 3등분한다.

3. 팽이버섯을 먹기 좋게 찢고, 쳥양고추는 잘게 다진다.

4. 프라이팬에 올리브유 두르고 두부와 대파를 노릇하게 구워서 접시에 덜어놓는다.

5. 프라이팬에 분량의 양념간장 만들어 팽이버섯 넣고 볶는다.

6. 접시에 두부, 대파, 팽이버섯 순으로 올리고 나머지 소스와 다진 청양고추 뿌리고 먹는다.

#두부요리 #두부구이 #팽이버섯요리 #두부팽이버섯 #두부간장조림 #초간단두부요리 #팽이버섯레시피

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. 두부 팽이버섯 계란국

✅ 재료
두부 반모 170g
팽이버섯 1봉
계란 2개 (소금, 후추 약간)
대파 한줌
청양고추 1개 (옵션)

✅ 양념
다시마 육수 800ml
된장 1스푼
국간장 1스푼
참치액 1스푼

7pxbGjvcdyY.title: Full Meeting between President Trump, VP Vance and Ukrainian President Zelenskyy in Oval Office
7pxbGjvcdyY.description:
A heated argument broke out between President Donald Trump, Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky, and Vice President JD Vance in the White House Oval Office. The confrontation occurred before a deal was supposed to be made between Ukraine and the United States in which Ukraine would give the U.S. critical minerals in exchange for some unspecified help in dealing with Russia's invasion. Trump and Vance accused Zelensky of being "disrespectful," ungrateful, and of gambling with starting a global war. Before the argument began, President Trump was asked by reporters if he would provide Ukraine with security guarantees, but he declined to affirmatively answer these questions. President Zelensky said Ukraine needed security guarantees and that a ceasefire would not be sufficient. A scheduled news conference between the two leaders was subsequently canceled after this meeting. https://www.c-span.org/event/white-house-event/president-trump-meets-with-ukrainian-president/431338

PKolOtesJts.title: Gene Hackman Death Investigation | Santa Fe County Sheriff's Office gives update on latest
PKolOtesJts.description:
Gene Hackman Found Dead: Oscar-winner Gene Hackman, his wife and one of their dogs were apparently dead for some time before a maintenance worker discovered their bodies at the couple's Santa Fe home, according to investigators.

Hackman, 95, was found dead Wednesday in a mudroom and his 65-year-old wife, Betsy Arakawa, was found in a bathroom next to a space heater, Santa Fe County Sheriff’s Office detectives wrote in a search warrant affidavit. There was an open prescription bottle and pills scattered on a countertop near Arakawa.

Santa Fe County Sheriff's Office gives an update on the death of Gene Hackman. Video from KOAT.

YZ1S3Jvegz4.description:
Prime Video India Presents 
Dupahiya Official Trailer  
Starring Gajraj Rao, Sparsh Shrivastava, Renuka Shahane, Bhuvan Arora, Shivani Raghuvanshi, Anjuman Saxena, Yashpal Sharma, Samarth Mahor, Komal Kushwaha 
Directed by Sonam Nair 
Creators and Executive Producers - Salona Bains Joshi and Shubh Shivdasani
Creators and Writers - Chirag Garg and Avinash Dwivedi
Production House - Bombay Film Cartel
 
Official Release Date Mar 7, 2025 on Prime Video India. 
 
About: 
Dhadakpur is the Belgium of Bihar. Clean, green and glorious. And this year the village will celebrate its Silver Jubilee of being crime- free! And as a gift for the villagers there will be a trophy, clean water but most of all pride. 
Also within 8 days, Roshni, the prettiest girl of the village will leave the Jha family and be wedded to Kuber. The plan was to marry his elder brother Durlabh, but the moment she heard that Durlabh’s younger brother works in Mumbai she didn’t even bat an eyelid to change the groom. Like her friends, Roshni too aspired for a modern city life.Her brother, Bhugol too has dreams of going to Mumbai and becoming a Bollywood superstar. 
 
The to-be-groom’s father is a clerk in the education department and Roshni’s dad, Banwari, is a temporary primary school teacher. This marriage meant his dream of a permanent job could be fulfilled. In short, everyone’s dreams hinge on this one wedding. But before their dreams could turn into reality, it was time to fulfill the to-be groom's dream. He wants a two-wheeler as a “wedding gift”. But not just any two-wheeler. A shiny red expensive motorbike! That too with a year’s supply of petrol. No one in Dhadakpur had paid such a handsome dowry before-but the Jha family is determined. 

The bike arrives in the day and disaster strikes at night. It got stolen! How? When? Who? There were only questions and no answers. Dhadakpur is crime-free after all! 
Leading the queue of suspects, was Roshni’s, ex-boyfriend, Amavas. Years ago, he was banished from Dhadakpur for his incessant stealing. 
Pushpalata Yadav, is Dhadakpur’s village head. It was her idea to banish Amavas from the village, but now he was their only hope. He could procure a second hand bike. 
Bhugol and Amavas are then sent to get the bike. Two childhood enemies. Chalk and cheese. Coffee and sleep. Ronaldo and The World Cup. How the two boys save the pride of the village and ensure the wedding happens as planned forms the crux of the season.

FYdffn1m0sQ.title: PSP Como Você NUNCA VIU!
FYdffn1m0sQ.description:
Confira a Alura: https://www.alura.com.br/brksedu
Cupom de desconto: BRKSEDU

Vídeo mostrando o PSP - PlayStation Portable - como você nunca viu! Nesse vídeo compartilho diversas capturas de gameplay feitas diretamente de um PSP-3000 japonês! Isso é possível pois o PSP-2000 e o PSP-3000 têm suporte a saída de áudio e vídeo, então consegui fazer capturas externas usando o cabo componente oficial do PSP, um RetroTink 4K e uma placa de captura da Avermedia modelo GC573.

O PSP foi o único console portátil que conseguiu bater de frente com a Nintendo. Foi um portátil que vendeu muito bem, teve diversos lançamentos excelentes, e funcionava também como media player. 

A mídia física do PSP era um disco chamado de UMD - Universal Media Disc. Existiam não apenas jogos em UMD mas também filmes e seriados.

Nesse vídeo trago games que foram marcantes no PSP, como LittleBigPlanet, Gran Turismo, Ridge Racer, Crisis Core Final Fantasy VII, Star Ocean Second Evolution, God of War Ghost of Sparta e mais!

wVbZzgybaJ4.title: Marvin Sapp: Tiny Desk Concert
wVbZzgybaJ4.description:
Ashley Pointer | February 28, 2025
The morning that Bishop Marvin Sapp came to NPR, he told me that it was his kids who really emphasized how important it was for him to accept our invitation to perform: "They told me, 'Dad, Tiny Desk is for the culture.' "

Backed by a four-piece band and a six-piece choir, Sapp transforms our office into a sanctuary, performing an 11-song medley of praise and worship hits that span more than three decades in music and ministry. From the moment his set begins, the spirit moves through the room, filling every corner with raw emotion, joy and reverence.

From Sapp's early days with the trailblazing '90s gospel group Commissioned to penning anthems like "Never Would Have Made It" — a song that transcends church walls — his impact is woven into the fabric of Black culture. "What's funny is, I saw some of y'all singing these songs, and y'all weren't even born when I recorded them," Sapp jokes, underscoring his intergenerational influence. Yet, despite his legendary status, Sapp took time after the performance to speak and pray with members of our audience, choosing ministry first, above all else.

3dQN0Bge7s8.title: Champions Trophy 2025 IND vs BAN: India से हारकर Bangladesh ने कराई अपने Fans की बेइज़्ज़ती, हुए roast
3dQN0Bge7s8.description:
Champions Trophy 2025 IND vs BAN: India से हारकर Bangladesh ने कराई अपने Fans की बेइज़्ज़ती, हुए roast

#championstrophy2025 #indiavsbangladesh #indvsban  

आईसीसी चैंपियंस ट्रॉफी 2025 में भारत अपने सभी मुकाबले दुबई में खेलेगा जबकि पाकिस्तान बाकी देशों की मेजबानी करेगा. टूर्नामेंट का आगाज 19 फरवरी से हो चुका है और भारतीय टीम अपने अभियान की शुरुआत 20 फरवरी से कर चुकी है. कुल 8 टीमों को दो ग्रुप में बांटा गया है. पहले ग्रुप में भारत, पाकिस्तान, न्यूजीलैंड और बांग्लादेश शामिल हैं. वहीं, दूसरे ग्रुप में साउथ अफ्रीका, अफगानिस्तान, ऑस्ट्रेलिया और इंग्लैंड की टीमें हैं. टूर्नामेंट का फाइनल मैच 9 मार्च को होगा. भारतीय टीम अपना पहला मुकाबला बांग्लादेश के खिलाफ 6 विकेट से जीत चुकी है. भारत और पाकिस्तान के बीच महामुकाबला 23 फरवरी को दुबई में खेला जाएगा. इसके बाद भारतीय टीम ग्रुप स्टेज का तीसरा और आखिरी मुकाबला 2 मार्च को न्यूजीलैंड के खिलाफ खेलेगी. दोनों ग्रुप की टॉप-2 टीमें सेमीफाइनल के लिए क्वालीफाई करेंगी. लेकिन पाकिस्तान की चुनौती से पहले, बांग्लादेश क्रिकेट टीम पर जीत अर्जित करते ही भारतीय क्रिकेट टीम ने एक अच्छी शुरुआत की है. इस जीत के बाद इंडियन क्रिकेट फैंस में भी ख़ुशी की लहर दौड़ गयी. बांग्लादेश की हार के बाद क्या कहा भारतीय फैंस ने? आगामी भारत बनाम पाकिस्तान मैच के लिए कितने उत्सुक हैं भारतीय फैंस? क्यों जारी कर रहे हैं भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम के लिए चेतावनी? बांग्लादेश क्रिकेट टीम के फैंस अब क्यों चाहते हैं पाकिस्तान क्रिकेट टीम को हराना? क्यों फूटा बांग्लादेशी फैंस का अपने कप्तान नजमुल होसैन शान्तो पर गुस्सा? भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस ने कैसे किया बांग्लादेशी फैंस का रोस्ट? जानने के लिए देखिये ज़ी स्विच के चयन रस्तोगी की ये खास वीडियो सीधे दुबई इंटरनैशनल क्रिकेट स्टेडियम से, जहां वो बात कर रहे हैं बांग्लादेशी क्रिकेट फैंस और भारतीय क्रिकेट फैंस से. 

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started on February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. A total of 8 teams have been divided into two groups. The first group includes India, Pakistan, New Zealand and Bangladesh. At the same time, the second group includes teams from South Africa, Afghanistan, Australia and England. The final match of the tournament will be held on March 9. The Indian team has won its first match against Bangladesh by 6 wickets. The great match between India and Pakistan will be played in Dubai on February 23. After this, the Indian team will play the third and last match of the group stage against New Zealand on March 2. The top-2 teams of both the groups will qualify for the semi-finals. But before the challenge of Pakistan, the Indian cricket team has made a good start as soon as it won over the Bangladesh cricket team. After this victory, a wave of happiness also ran among the Indian cricket fans. What did the Indian fans say after Bangladesh's defeat? How eager are Indian fans for the upcoming India vs Pakistan match? Why are Indian cricket fans issuing warnings to Pakistan cricket team? Why do Bangladesh cricket team fans now want to defeat Pakistan cricket team? Why are Bangladeshi fans angry with their captain Nazmul Hossain Shanto? To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch's Chayan Rastogi directly from Dubai International Cricket Stadium, where he is talking to Bangladeshi cricket fans and Indian cricket fans.

Le 29 octobre 1956, Israël lance une invasion contre l’Egypte. Deux jours plus tard, la France et le Royaume-Uni choque le monde en attaquant à leur tour l’Egypte... mais si l'opération militaire est une réussite, c'est un fiasco diplomatique. Un cuisant revers qui va marquer la fin de la suprématie européenne sur le monde.

15% de réduction sur votre eSIM Saily avec le code NEOXI

Le 13 janvier 2012, le Costa Concordia, un paquebot de croisière immense, chavire au large de l'île du Giglio, en Italie. Une nuit qui tourne au drame pour des milliers de passagers et qui laisse des traces indélébiles dans l’histoire maritime. Comme toujours, j’aime vous emmener au cœur des grandes catastrophes qui ont marqué les esprits. Dans cette vidéo, je reviens sur cette nuit fatidique : des erreurs humaines, des décisions qui ont tout changé et des histoires humaines bouleversantes. Paroles :

J’suis plus qu’un rappeur, j’suis un écrivain 
Quand j’veux entendre un disque, j’en écris un 
J’suis un bovin, élevé au grain 
Pas comme ces MC’s allaités aux faux seins 
Chronique 2001, dans la mémoire 
À l’époque où le meilleur rappeur était un blanc et le meilleur golfeur était un noir 
Ils disent que l’rap est mort mais qu’Tupac est toujours en vie 
J’serais pas surpris d’le voir un d’ces jours en ville 
J’lis leurs biographies en lecture rapide, j’aurais dû congeler les ovules de Mélanie Mais nique les clones, on n’a pas les mêmes codes 
C’est moi l’inspecteur académique de Nouvelle École 
La première chose qu’un rappeur doit faire, c’est de trouver une autre source de revenu Quitter la rue, trouver une sécu, serrer la ceinture tout au début 
Jamais cé-us pour une couverture, pour être à la une de la cover iTunes, garder sa nature mais faire des tunes 
Bellek aux stats, aux média-rap, la plupart d’entre eux sont des rats de star Ce sont nos fans qui mettent dans des cases, qui ne sont que des arbitres de catch Puristes de base qui jouent les DA, comme un téléphone fixe qui fait des snaps Pour eux faut qu’tu saches, une carrière qui marche, c’est quand ça dépasse la durée de vie d’une brique de lait d’vache 
N’aie pas la haine cousin, c’est moi leur N+1 
Le dernier bouquin qu’ils ont lu, c’est le livre d’entretien de l’Audi A1 
Eux et moi ça fait deux, frère, on s’rappelle plus d’eux comme FFP2 
J’écoute pas leur album deux fois, j’écoute leurs albums en x2 
Les producteurs sont des rappeurs ratés, mais c’est aussi l’cas de la plupart des rappeurs 
Ils pensent qu’à niquer les consommateurs, ils portent leurs préservatifs sur le cœur 
Les patrons d’majors, on les préfère bouche fermée mais chéquier ouvert 
J’vais ouvrir un numéro vert, faire l’inventaire de ces gros pervers 
J’arrive, un, deux, trois, reste en croix, juste avant je les ai laissés croire Eux y ont cessé d’croître dans leur crâne, leur carrière dans le fond d’un C3 Leur carrière dans le fond d’un G7, l’ingé son, l’ingé sait, l’ingé saigne Container CGM CMA dans la mémoire de mon GSM, Stentor 
Putain j’aime trop les cuivres, putain j’aime trop le peura 
J’ai gagné des points d’vie, j’ai gagné des points d’aura 
Je n’sais que me battre, je n’sais que les battre, je n’sais que les bastonner C’est pas que du rap, c’est gros QI rap, et toi tu rappes pas dans les temps Faut clearer le sample et la créance à la SACEM 
Je sais qu’le temps m’a grisé les tempes, c’est pas pour autant qu’j’les monte pas en l’air
Tu sais petit, que tous les ans j’suis dans le casting des “11 rappeurs à suivre” 
Mon management, c’est l’plus influent, dans l’top 100, c’est l’premier d’la liste 90 BPM, mon cœur bat sur le rythme, et même quand je pleure, je pleure en rime 
La cérémonie des Flammes se termine à minuit, mais l’mariage au rap c’est pour la vie 
Faut pas qu’tu t’inquiètes, si t’es quelqu’un dans la fame, au canon silencieux je te dead Gros QI rap dans la tête, pas là pour être un mème ou une trend 
20 ans d’carrière et crois-moi, j’vais pas lâcher 
Si j’marchais sur l’eau, les journalistes diraient j’sais pas nager 
Quand j’dis "El Hamdoulillah", ces connards me disent "à tes souhaits" T’as mis 100 ans à pousser, j’vais mettre 20 minutes à te scier 
C’est que du rap conscient, t’as jamais l’compte en banque en excédent Y’a que Michael Jackson qu’est passé de pauvre et noir à riche et blanc Y’aura bien plus de gens quand on va me pendre qu’à mon 
couronnement Veuillez laisser l’rap en sortant comme il était propre en rentrant, merci.

Mind ©️

Pn6e1O5bEyA.title: Starship | Seventh Flight Test
Pn6e1O5bEyA.description:
The first Starship flight test of 2025 flew with ambitious goals: seeking to repeat our previous success of launching and catching the world’s most powerful launch vehicle while putting a redesigned and upgraded Starship through a rigorous set of flight demonstrations.

It served as a reminder that development testing, by definition, can be unpredictable.

On its seventh flight test, Starship successfully lifted off from Starbase in Texas at 4:37 p.m. CT on Thursday, January 16. For the second time ever, the Super Heavy booster returned to the launch site and was caught by the tower. But before Starship could reach space, a fire developed in the aft section leading to a rapid unscheduled disassembly.

As always, success comes from what we learned, and this flight test will help us improve Starship’s reliability as SpaceX seeks to make life multiplanetary.

v_kTNIYsFnQ.title: Full argument: Trump-Zelensky White House meeting descends into shouting match
v_kTNIYsFnQ.description:
Donald Trump’s Oval Office meeting with Volodymyr Zelensky descended into a shouting match with the US president abruptly ending the conversation and throwing reporters out.

Mr Trump told the Ukrainian president he was “gambling with World War Three” as their meeting became heated.

The Ukrainian president told Mr Trump the rare earth minerals deal being negotiated by the two leaders was not enough for his country.

Mr Trump in turn accused Mr Zelensky of being “very disrespectful”.

 JD Vance, the vice president, intervened, asking Mr Zelensky: “have you said thank you once?”

As voices were raised, Mr Trump told the Ukrainian leader that “you have to be thankful”.

“You either make a deal, or we are out,” the president warned.

Mr Trump then abruptly ended the meeting saying he thought it was enough, with the press abruptly ushered out.

UzfVjgZKjro.title: Wie soziale Medien unseren Wahlkampf beeinflussen | ZDF Magazin Royale
UzfVjgZKjro.description:
Eine Perle der deutschen Innovationskunst: die Litfaßsäule. Seit über hundert Jahren trägt sie tapfer die Plakate von Musikstars, Monstertruck-Shows oder Parteien. Aber die Grand Dame des Marketings hat ein typisch deutsches Problem: die Digitalisierung. Unser Wahlkampf findet inzwischen auch im Internet statt. Und da gibt es keine deutsche Infrastruktur, also verlassen sich die Parteien auf die Social-Media-Plattformen aus den USA oder China. Für die Parteien ist das super, hier können sie personalisierte Wahlwerbung – mit Microtargeting – schalten, anstatt darauf zu hoffen, dass irgendwelche Menschen das halbzerissene Wahlplakat an der Litfaßsäule sehen. Win-win für die Parteien und Plattformen, aber auch für die Wähler*innen?

q9hq9UA9seI.title: Das ukrainische Fegefeuer
q9hq9UA9seI.description:
Fast 1.100 Tage nach dem russischen Einmarsch zeichnet sich eine klare Tendenz ab. Militärexperte Markus Reisner vergleicht den Konflikt mit einem Boxkampf „David vs. Goliath“: Der agile David (David Haye) verpasst den entscheidenden „Lucky Punch“, während der längere Atem des massigen Goliath (Nikolai Walujew) zunehmend zu dessen Vorteil wird.
Reisner analysiert die Lage an verschiedenen Kriegsschauplätzen und beleuchtet den beiderseitigen Einsatz von Drohnen. Abschließend geht er auf die Münchner Sicherheitskonferenz, aktuelle Aussagen von US-Präsident Trump und deren mögliche Folgen ein – mit ernüchternden Perspektiven für die Ukraine und Europa.

Wenn sie ein Talent in ihr Team holen möchten, drücken sie auf den Buzzer und der Sänger oder die Sängerin ist eine Runde weiter. Falls mehrere Coaches buzzern, hat das Talent freie Wahl. 

Nach den Blind Auditions folgen die Knockouts. Dort werden jeweils 12 Talents in drei Gruppen unterteilt, in denen sie ihren Coach in direkter Konkurrenz überzeugen müssen. 

Nur wer sich hier abermals durchsetzt, schafft es in die alles ersehnten Finals - und hier entscheidet sich letztendlich, welches Talent welchen Teams mit einer atemberaubenden Stimme überzeugen kann und "The Voice Kids" gewinnt!

Bei "The Voice Kids" dürfen die jüngsten Talente zeigen, was in ihnen steckt! Dabei zählt nur die Stimme: Denn während ihres Auftritts in den Blind Auditions sind die Coach-Sessel in Richtung des Publikums ausgerichtet, sodass die Coaches nicht sehen, wer auf der Bühne steht.

Wenn sie ein Talent in ihr Team holen möchten, drücken sie auf den Buzzer und der Sänger oder die Sängerin ist eine Runde weiter. Falls mehrere Coaches buzzern, hat das Talent freie Wahl. 

Nach den Blind Auditions folgen die Knockouts. Dort werden jeweils 12 Talents in drei Gruppen unterteilt, in denen sie ihren Coach in direkter Konkurrenz überzeugen müssen. 

Nur wer sich hier abermals durchsetzt, schafft es in die alles ersehnten Finals - und hier entscheidet sich letztendlich, welches Talent welchen Teams mit einer atemberaubenden Stimme überzeugen kann und "The Voice Kids" gewinnt!

Ohne Zweifel wird diese Technik die konventionelle Wärmepumpe für immer ablösen.

Verblüffenderweise ist der Schlüssel zu diesen erstaunlichen Spezifikationen jedoch dieses unscheinbare Material hier.

8TU0caL30os.title: Frust und Sorge – Planlos vor der Bundestagswahl | Y-Kollektiv
8TU0caL30os.description:
Die Reportage "Scheiße, wen wähle ich?" könnt ihr jetzt schon in der ARD Mediathek streamen: https://1.ard.de/y-kollektiv_bundestagswahl?premiere
----------
Y-Reporter Frederik Fleig weiß kurz vor der Wahl noch nicht, wem er seine Stimme geben soll – und damit ist er nicht allein. Viele in seiner Generation sind unentschlossen. Wir leben in Krisenzeiten: Die Wirtschaft schwächelt, vor unserer Haustür tobt ein Krieg, und die politischen Debatten sind aufgeheizt.

Was denken junge Menschen vor der Wahl? Was frustriert sie, und was wünschen sie sich?

Um das herauszufinden, reist Frederik Fleig für eine Woche in eine Region, die schon immer ein Schmelztiegel war – und in der er selbst studiert und gearbeitet hat: den Ruhrpott. Hier gab es schon immer große soziale Konflikte, große Probleme, aber auch große Träume.
In Duisburg, Bochum und Gelsenkirchen trifft Frederik auf junge Menschen, die nun AfD statt SPD wählen – und auf Menschen, die Angst vor einem Rechtsruck haben.

#australia #wealth #money 

------

Every year up until its collapse, Credit Suisse would prepare a report that looked at how wealthy the people of countries around the world were. 
Instead of just looking at GDP per capita which calculates how much the average person in an economy produces in market output every year, this report attempted to calculate the net worth of those people to see how good they were at accumulating wealth over time. 
Someone with a high income that is spending everything they make on rent and overpriced food isn’t going to grow their wealth as quickly as someone who has a more modest income, but is paying off their own home and is investing diligently into retirement accounts.
I like to call this the San Fran Tech Bro Conjecture. 
But according to these annual reports the Australian people always looked like that second group of slower more deliberate wealth builders.
Their raw income isn’t as high as here in America, but they were consistently some of the wealthiest people on the planet. 
UBS, which absorbed Credit Suisse following its collapse, recently released the 2024 report and once again Australians had the second highest MEDIAN net worth on the planet. 
They only fell behind Luxembourg which is a European Micronation which you are probably not in the tax bracket to even be aware of. 
The fact that this report tracks the MEDIAN instead of the average net worth is also really important. 
This means that the Australian right in the middle of a line up from richest to poorest is more than TWICE as rich as an American in the same position…

eWjz0eiwJ-0.title: FC Bayern München – Eintracht Frankfurt | Bundesliga, 23. Spieltag 2024/25 | sportstudio
eWjz0eiwJ-0.description:
Bundesliga-Spitzenreiter FC Bayern München bleibt auch ohne den verletzt ausgewechselten Anführer Joshua Kimmich klar auf Meisterkurs. Im Topspiel besiegten die wieder frischer wirkenden Münchner den Tabellendritten Eintracht Frankfurt souverän mit 4:0 (1:0).

Hier gibt es die Highlights der Bundesliga, der UEFA Champions League und des DFB-Pokals. Dazu die Highlights ausgewählter Partien der 2. Bundesliga und der Frauen-Bundesliga. Abonniert hier den Kanal: https://kurz.zdf.de/abosport/

Das Bundesliga-Spitzenspiel zwischen Bayer Leverkusen und dem FC Bayern München hat gezeigt, wie dominant die Werkself gegen Bayern auftreten kann. Leverkusen hat sich im Kampf um die Schale als Hauptkonkurrent von Bayern München etabliert. Und könnten auch in der Champions League die Bayern ausbremsen. Aber wie abhängig ist Leverkusen wirklich von seinem Star-Coach? Das schauen wir uns im neuen Bolzplatz an: https://kurz.zdf.de/uDFZ/

sportstudio bei Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/sportstudio/
sportstudio bei TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@sportstudio.de
sportstudio bei WhatsApp: https://kurz.zdf.de/6Em3U/

Die Eintracht begann respektlos und attackierte die Münchner so früh und entschlossen in deren Hälfte, dass es umgehend energischer Anweisungen von Trainer Vincent Kompany bedurfte - seine Armbewegung signalisierte: raus da hinten! Dies gelang seiner Mannschaft zunehmend, unter anderem, weil sie ihrerseits viel engagierter und entschlossener ins Gegenpressing ging und kam, als dies zuletzt der Fall war. Nach einer Chance für Hugo Ekitiké (6.) sahen sich die Frankfurter mehr und mehr zurückgedrängt, es ergaben sich zahlreiche Gelegenheiten für die Bayern: Die beste verhinderte Rasmus Kristensen, der Jamal Musialas Schuss auf der Torlinie blockte (15.). Die Münchner kombinierten nun gut, waren klar überlegen, immer wieder aber stand dem Torerfolg ein Körperteil eines Frankfurters im Weg.
Die Eintracht tauchte dafür nur noch selten in der Hälfte der Münchner auf. Die Konter liefen in der Regel über Ansgar Knauff, sie blieben aber weitgehend ungefährlich. Für die größte Aufregung bei den Bayern sorgte so zunächst kurz vor der Pause Kimmich, der ohne Einwirkung eines Gegenspielers zu Boden ging und offenbar wegen einer Fußverletzung ausgewechselt werden musste (42.). Joshua Kimmich, der bis dahin keine Minute Spielzeit in dieser Saison verpasst hatte, wurde ersetzt durch Leon Goretzka. Und der neue Mann leitete sogleich den Führungstreffer ein: ein Pass auf Musiala, ein Pass auf Leroy Sané, ein Querpass auf Michael Olise – Tor (45.+3). Die beiden Flügelspieler waren die auffälligsten Offensivakteure der Münchner. 

Mit zunehmender Spielzeit konnten sich die Bayern darauf konzentrieren, Ball und Gegner zu kontrollieren. Sie taten dies in sehr seriöser Manier. Auch nach dem Tor von Hiroki Ito (61.), der nach einem Eckball traf. Der Japaner wurde danach umgehend ausgewechselt. Leroy Sané (78.) vergab zwar erst freistehend eine Riesenchance, dann räumte Musiala (83.) aber alle Zweifel aus - und verließ nach seinem Treffer leicht angeschlagen das Feld. In der Nachspielzeit stellte Serge Gnabry für den Rekordmeister noch auf 4:0 (90.+2).

Während die SPD ihr schlechtestes Wahlergebnis seit der Nachkriegszeit erzielt hat, erhielt die Union unter Friedrich Merz knapp 30 Prozent der Stimmen. Trotzdem ist die AfD der heimliche Gewinner, denn sie konnte ihren Wähleranteil verdoppeln. Überraschung des Abends war Die Linke. Die Partei, die nach Abgang von Sahra Wagenknecht totgesagt wurde, konnte ein Comeback machen. Anders sieht es beim Bündnis Sahra Wagenknecht (BSW) aus. Das BSW verpasst den Einzug in den Bundestag nur knapp. Ebenfalls nicht im Bundestag vertreten ist die FDP. Deren Chef Christian Lindner ist am selben Abend noch zurückgetreten. Welche Konsequenzen bei der SPD gezogen werden, ist noch unklar. Die Ära von Olaf Scholz ist auf jeden Fall vorbei.

wIhFVtgMcW8.title: Unschätzbar: Loh-Collection mit 9 Mio. CLK GTR 🤩💸 | GRIP
wIhFVtgMcW8.description:
Dietzhölztal im beschaulichen Mittelhessen: Wer hierher kommt, ahnt nicht, dass sich in dieser ländlichen Idylle eines der unglaublichsten Automuseen der Welt befindet: „The Loh Collection“. Und GRIP erhält exklusiv eine Führung vom Gründer persönlich! Matthias Malmedie besucht Friedhelm Loh, seines Zeichens Unternehmer, Philanthrop - und leidenschaftlicher Autosammler. Über 35 Jahre lang hat er die schönsten und seltensten Fahrzeuge der Welt zusammengetragen und präsentiert sie jetzt in einem eigenen Museum der Weltöffentlichkeit! Matthias will dem „Menschen“ Friedhelm Loh näherkommen, möchte seine persönliche Geschichte und seine Autoleidenschaft kennenlernen. Außerdem darf der GRIP-Testfahrer besondere Schmuckstückstücke aus der Sammlung tatsächlich selbst fahren, darunter auch einen Mercedes-Benz CLK GTR mit satten 631 PS. Es ist der Prototyp einer Kleinserie von nur 25 Autos. Diese werden heute mit bis zu 9 Millionen Euro gehandelt. Aber den Prototyp gibt es ja nur ein einziges Mal. Sein Wert: unschätzbar. In dieser Sammlung gerät Matthias komplett außer Rand und Band, so hat man ihn noch nie gesehen...

Die Idee: Schnell günstigen Wohnraum mit Schulen, Kindergärten und Läden für alle schaffen. Aber seit den 90ern sind die Blocks vor allem im Straßenrap zum Symbol für Tristesse geworden. Also: Warum heißt der Plattenbau eigentlich Plattenbau? Wieso hat jede Stadt heute ihre eigene Betonsiedlung? Und warum sieht man Blocks gefühlt in jedem zweiten Musikvideo?

In der neuen HYPECULTURE Folge gehen wir von New York nach Paris, über Marseille und Neapel in die DDR. Und in jede westdeutsche Kleinstadt, in der es einen Block am Stadtrand gibt. Wir erklären, wie der Traum vom “Wohnen für Alle” scheitern konnte und wofür der Plattenbau heute steht. Und wir fragen: Hat die Platte jetzt ihr Comeback?
